name: Almighty Alpacas
description: Almighty Alpacas are the main characters in Alpaca Dash, which is the flagship Race & Earn game from the DeFi Land team. Alpaca Dash is a one-of-a-kind PvP game with amazing dynamics, including unlockable skill trees, various racing tracks, and unique quests. Each Alpaca has five general stats and hidden genetics, which you can explore by actively playing the game. Almighty Alpacas feature beautiful art and upcoming surprises for the holders. Join the almighty march to the future!
